                      "color": "#f0f3f5"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\n"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "kind": "paragraph",
                  "align": "left",
                  "inlines": [
                    {
                      "text": "This project will be presented in two distinct phases, each related to unique features that contributed to the final product.",
